Prison Rodeo Programs
Coverage
Huntsville, Texas
Date
Description

The Prison Rodeo Program, Official Souvenir booklet, includes 84 pages of photographs depicting the 52nd Annual Prison Rodeo held in Huntsville, Texas, including photographs of the Texas Board of Corrections, features and articles for events and performances, and photographs of the facilities within the prison.
